channel.title: I Need To Make Money xD
channel.description:
Ok, I need to buy my mum a birthday present, but I need to buy it off E-bay. I only need 7 dollars more but I got the other 60 dollars from my dad. He wont give me anymore. How can I make money over the net? I need an easy way.
Also, I'm selling a GameRenders forum PREMIUM account that has 3 reputation. It has access to thousands or Photoshop add ons that a free account cannot access! I also have released 3 video tutorials in the tutorials section that I am getting rep for nearly everyday :)
If you are interested in the account, PM me or add me on b00mh3adsh0t@hotmail.co.uk to talk about the sale. Looking for 7 dollars, or course xD
